contentrichtext.text: '''OSX''' may also refer to: ==Technology== *[[OS X]], an operating system family for [[Apple, Inc|Apple]] computers. *[[DC/OSx]], 1980s-era Unix operating system by Pyramid Technology *[[X Window System]] ==Other== *[[Kosciusko-Attala County Airport]] in [[Kosciusko, Mississippi]], by IATA code *OSX, a Brazilian shipbuilding company, part of the [[EBX Group]] *[[Old Saxon]], an early form of Low German used until the 12th century, by ISO 639-3 language code ==See also== *{{lookfrom|OSX}} *{{intitle|OSX}} {{disambig}} [[ja:OS X]]
